import React, { useState } from 'react'; import axios from 'axios'; function LoanForm() { const [formData, setFormData] = useState({ Full_Name: '', Address: '', PAN_Number: '', Company_Name: '', Current_Salary: 0, Previous_Salary: 0, Owns_House: '', Rent_Amount: 0, Grocery_Expense: 0, Current_EMIs: 0, Date_Previous_Hike: '', Date_Next_Hike: '', Bank_Name: '', Credit_Score: 0, Number_of_Credit_Cards: 0, Total_Credit_Limit: 0, Number_of_Loans: 0, Employment_Duration: '', Job_Title: '', Bonuses_Allowances: 0, Savings: 0, Investments: 0, Monthly_Expenses: 0, Age: 0, Education_Level: '', Marital_Status: '', Dependents: 0, Loan_Purpose: '', Requested_Loan_Amount: 0, Preferred_Repayment_Period: 0, Mall_Visits_Per_Month: 0, Mall_Spend_Average: 0 }); const handleChange = (e) => { const { name, value } = e.target; setFormData({ ...formData, [name]: value }); }; const handleSubmit = async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); try { const response = await axios.post('http://localhost:5000/predict', formData); console.log(response.data); // Handle the response data alert(`Prediction Result: \nEligibility: ${response.data.Eligibility}\nRequested Loan Amount: ${response.data.Requested_Loan_Amount}\nPreferred Repayment Period: ${response.data.Preferred_Repayment_Period}\nEMI: ${response.data.EMI}\nRisk Score: ${response.data.Risk_Score}`); } catch (error) { console.error("There was an error!", error); } }; return (
); } export default LoanForm;
